Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20世紀福斯  夢工廠影業\N聯合奉獻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:01:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紮努克公司  出品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領銜主演: 湯姆·漢克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領銜主演: 保羅·紐曼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領銜主演: 裘德·洛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs28\bord1\shad1\4a&H80&\b0片名: 毀 滅 之 路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many stories about Michael Sullivan.\N麥克·蘇利文的故事多到說不完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some say he was a decent man.\N有人說他為人正直
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some say there was no good in him at all.\N有人說他一無是處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I once spent six weeks on the road with him...\N1931年冬天  我曾和他一同旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the winter of 1931.\N六個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our story.\N這是我們的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主演: 詹妮弗·傑森·李
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主演: 斯坦利·圖齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主演: 丹尼爾·克雷格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir. Much obliged. Man dies in factory accident!\N謝謝  感謝您  工廠奪命意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs24\bord1\shad1\4a&H80&\pos(192,40)\b0主演: 泰勒·霍奇林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your paper here! Hot off the press, only 5 cents!\N買份快報  剛出版的  只要五分錢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主演: 連姆·艾肯   狄倫·貝克   塞倫·希德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選角: 黛布拉·贊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本片改編自同名繪本小說   作者:馬克斯·艾倫·柯林斯   插畫: 理查·皮爾斯·雷納
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音樂: 湯瑪斯·紐曼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服裝設計: 亞伯特·沃斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剪輯: 吉爾·比爾科克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs24\bord1\shad1\4a&H80&\pos(192,40)\b0藝術指導: 鄧尼斯·蓋斯納
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mr. Miller.\N謝謝  米勒先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攝影: 康拉德·L·赫爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,執行製片: 沃爾特·F·帕克斯   瓊·布拉德肖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,製片: 理查·D·紮努克   迪恩·紮努克   薩姆·門德斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,編劇: 大衛·塞歐夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導演: 薩姆·門德斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you with it later.\N等一下我再教你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go fetch your father.\N去叫你爸下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa?\N爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.\N吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bless us, O Lord, for thy gifts we are about to receive...\N感謝主  賜予我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...through the bounty of Jesus Christ, our Lord. Amen.\N豐盛的食物與耶穌的愛  阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Michael? - Sir?\N- 麥克  - 什麼事  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wake, so I don't want to see those dice.\N我們是去參加喪禮  所以不准玩骰子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.\N不會的  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.\N哈囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna go.\N我不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come on, it's all right. - No. I'm scared.\N- 走啦  沒關係  - 我會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice helps preserve the body.\N冰塊有助於保存屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...\N那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who's got a hug for a lonely old man?\N誰願意給孤單老人一個擁抱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, which is which? Don't help me.\N我來猜誰是誰  不要告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Peter and Michael. - No!\N- 彼得和麥克  - 錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie, Mike, good to see you.\N安妮  麥克  你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you bring the necessary? - Yes.\N- 你帶吃飯的傢伙了嗎? - 帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me, I have urgent business with these young gentlemen.\N抱歉  我跟兩位小紳士有要事要商量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah! - Winner!\N- 贏了  - 贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the cops! I know hustlers when I see them.\N叫員警  你們耍老千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't hustle, old-timer. - Pay the man.\N- 沒有耍老千  老先生  - 付錢給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upstairs. Jacket pocket, in my study.\N到樓上書房的外衣口袋拿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I change my mind.\N快  免得我改變主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello? - Hello.\N- 哈囉  - 哈囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remind me, which little Sullivan are you?\N你是蘇利文的哪個兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Michael, sir. - Sir? You don't have to call me sir.\N- 麥克  先生  - 先生  不必叫我先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your pa.\N我不是你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mr. Rooney.\N不行  那叫隆尼先生好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Connor.\N叫我康諾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, call me Uncle Connor.\N不  叫我康諾叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?\N你有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rooney sent me to get his jacket.\N隆尼先生叫我來拿外套
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You come back later, huh?\N等會再來  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy.\N我正在忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Sir.\N好的  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, hello.\N哈囉  哈囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to welcome all of you to my home.\N歡迎各位來到寒舍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to have so many friends in this house again.\N各位朋友齊聚一堂真叫我高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Mary died, it's....\N自從瑪麗死後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just been me and my boy rattling around in these rooms.\N只剩我和我兒子整日游走在這棟房子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had this speech prepared, but it would be...\N我原本準備了一篇講稿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...dishonest of me to say that I knew Danny well.\N說我熟識丹尼可能不盡真實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:11:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lose one of us, it hurts us all.\N但任何人走了  大家都難過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what I do remember, though, and Finn will remember this too...\N我來談談我記得的幾件事  相信芬恩也記得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's Danny on the high school football team.\N丹尼是高中橄欖球校隊的球員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A championship game. Down six points, 10 seconds left to play...\N冠軍賽中  落後六分  只剩10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...four yards to go, Danny tackles his own quarterback.\N還有四碼要攻  可丹尼卻擒倒了自家的四分衛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistakes, you know.... We all make them. God knows.\N犯錯人人難免  上帝看在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink to Danny's honor.\N為丹尼的榮耀喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wake him to God and hope that he gets to heaven...\N讓我們守護他進入天國
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at least an hour before the devil finds out he's dead.\N在惡魔發現之前交到上帝手中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Amen. - To Danny!\N- 阿門  - 敬丹尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I would like to ask a dear and a trusted friend...\N現在請我們忠心的老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Finn McGovern, to say a few words...\N芬恩·麥高文跟我們講幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...words that I'll wager got more poetry than mine.\N他比我更善於表達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get over here.\N請過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, John.\N謝謝你  約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My brother Danny wasn't wise.\N我的兄弟丹尼並不聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor was he gentle.\N也並不溫柔體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with a skinful of liquor in him, he was a pain in the ass.\N三杯黃湯下肚  算得上是號麻煩人物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was loyal and brave.\N但是  他忠貞不二勇敢無比
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he never told a lie.\N終其一生未曾說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd have enjoyed this party.\N他應該也會喜歡這次聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and the family, we wanna say thank you to our generous host.\N我和其他家人想向你這位慷慨的主人道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where would this town be without Mr. John Rooney?"\N本鎮虧欠約翰·隆尼太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've worked for you for many years now, John.\N我為你效忠多年了  約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nearly half my life.\N幾乎是我的半輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we've never had a disagreement.\N我們從未有過爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to realize that you rule this town...\N我終於瞭解你的領導風格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as God rules the earth.\N簡直是人間的上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You give, and you take away-- - Lovely. Lovely speech.\N- 凡他賜予的終將回歸於他  - 太美了  講得太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bury my brother. Then I'm gonna deal with you.\N等我安葬了兄弟  我再找你算帳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, Finn, sure.\N沒問題  芬恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll take care of all of us.\N我們大家都受你照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get a good night's sleep.\N先好好睡一覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He all right? - Yeah, he's fine.\N- 他還好吧  - 還好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just too much to drink.\N只是喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to him.\N我會找他談談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Take Mike with you. - No, Pa--\N- 帶麥克跟你一起去  - 不  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Mike with you.\N帶麥克跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just talk, nothing more.\N只是談談  沒別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always smiling?\N為什麼你老是掛著笑臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause it's all so fucking hysterical.\N因為這一切簡直瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael.\N麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a nightmare. It was about Mr. Rooney's house.\N我作了個惡夢  夢到隆尼先生的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a house.\N還不就是棟房子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big house.\N好大的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to sleep.\N回去睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mr. Rooney rich like the Babe?\N隆尼先生和棒球巨星貝勃一樣有錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richer.\N比他更有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we rich?\N我們有錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stupid.\N當然不  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's papa's job?\N爸爸的職業是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He works for Mr. Rooney.\N他替隆尼先生辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\N為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Papa didn't have a father...\N爸爸沒有父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so Mr. Rooney looked after him.\N所以隆尼先生照顧他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but what's his job?\N這我知道  但他是做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He goes on missions for Mr. Rooney.\N他幫隆尼先生解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very dangerous. That's why he brings his gun.\N因為很危險  所以他帶著槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes even the president sends him on missions...\N有時連總統都請他辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...'cause Papa was a war hero and all.\N因為爸爸是個戰爭英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're just making that up. - I am not.\N- 你亂講  - 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all so fucking hysterical.\N這一切簡直瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter, I can't come to your concert tonight. I'm working.\N彼得  我今晚不能參加你的音樂會  我得工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working at what?\N做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting food on your plate, young man.\N讓你不必餓勝子  年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, boys, come on, clear the plates.\N好啦  小夥子們  收拾餐具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good lad.\N好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You want a shot? - No.\N- 要不要來一口  - 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just talking to him, right?\N我們只跟他談談  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.\N當然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong, Finn. I feel for you. I do.\N別誤會  芬恩  我懂你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let a thing like that give you cause to go mouthing off.\N但你沒必要含沙射影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and my dad, you go back many years...\N你跟我爸相識多年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he is a just man.\N他是個可敬的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you say?\N你有什麼話要說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, Finn.\N表達點意見嘛  芬恩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make this easy.\N以免弄得太尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hear you.\N我們聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right. - Good.\N- 就聽你們的  - 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:24:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry. I'm sorry for your loss. I'm sorry for this misunderstanding.\N抱歉  抱歉你失去親人  抱歉引起這場誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sorry your brother was such a fucking liar.\N很抱歉  你兄弟是個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- My brother was not a liar. - Excuse me?\N- 我兄弟不是騙子  - 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.53,0:24:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect my family and keep my job, I'll stay quiet.\N為了家人和飯碗  我會閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't think I don't know something's going on.\N但我知道事有蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.53,0:24:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't think I won't find out what it is. - Whoa, buddy--\N- 而且我一定會查出來  - 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.95,0:24:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy.\N別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy.\N別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.37,0:24:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just talking. You tell your father my brother never stole from him.\N我們只是聊聊  跟你爸說  丹尼沒坑他的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've checked the books. He never sold booze to no one. lt's all accounted for.\N我查過帳冊  他沒有偷賣過一滴酒  每一桶都記得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.38,0:24:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- If he sold it, where's the money? - Fuck should I know?\N- 如果他賣了酒  那麼錢在哪  - 我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.34,0:24:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Did you check his mattress? -Maybe you should check yours.\N- 查查他床鋪底下  - 或許你該查查你自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.43,0:24:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something immoral here, don't you think, Mike?\N他這什麼態度  麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.22,0:24:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved father throws your undeserving little brother...\N我父親幫你那不成材的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.94,0:24:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the wake of his life, and this-- This is your thank-you?\N辦個體面的喪禮  這就是你的謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.77,0:24:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What a hideous world this is. - You think you're so smart.\N- 這世界反啦  - 你自以為聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.78,0:24:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think we don't know? You're spending so much time in Chicago--\N以為我們不知道你在芝加哥混
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.22,0:25:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?\N你怎麼那麼衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.93,0:25:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of here.\N快走
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.26,0:25:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ, Connor, what the hell are you thinking?!\N你到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.45,0:25:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus.\N噢  天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.78,0:25:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael.\N麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.62,0:25:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?\N你受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.25,0:25:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw everything?\N你都看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.97,0:26:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus.\N老天
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.39,0:26:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not to speak of this to anyone. You understand?\N這件事絕不可以說出去  懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.06,0:26:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to anyone!\N誰都不准說
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.48,0:26:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?\N他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.36,0:26:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of yours?\N你的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.82,0:26:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been hiding in the car.\N他一定是躲在車裡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.82,0:26:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can he keep a secret?\N他會保守秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.99,0:26:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my son.\N他是我兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.66,0:26:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's good enough for me.\N那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.13,0:26:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take him home.\N帶他回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.38,0:26:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think I'll walk.\N我走路回去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.92,0:26:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect night for a stroll.\N今晚最適合散步
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.58,0:27:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Mama know?\N媽媽知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.71,0:27:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother knows I love Mr. Rooney.\N你媽媽知道我愛隆尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.59,0:27:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had nothing.\N當我們一無所有時
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.01,0:27:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave us a home, a life. We owe him.\N他給了我們一個家  一份像樣的生活  我們虧欠他
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.23,0:27:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?\N你懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.00,0:27:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?\N你懂不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.36,0:27:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N懂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.78,0:27:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come on inside, then.\N進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.80,0:28:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys, clear your plates, please.\N孩子們  請收拾自己的碗盤
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.89,0:28:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it later.\N待會兒再收
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.43,0:28:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's time for school now-- - It's only a plate!\N- 要上學了  - 只不過是個盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.66,0:29:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing here?\N他來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.16,0:29:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael was hiding in the car...\N昨晚我出去時
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.41,0:29:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I went out last night.\N麥克躲在車裡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.79,0:29:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus, Mike.\N天啊  麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.46,0:29:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've spoken to him. It won't happen again.\N我跟他說過了  絕不再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.80,0:29:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom. Mom!\N媽  媽
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.02,0:29:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the feller...\N正是你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.35,0:29:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our secret, right?\N我們之間的秘密  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.53,0:29:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the dice.\N我是說賭骰子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.53,0:29:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man of honor always pays his debts.\N君子有債必還
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.37,0:29:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And keeps his word.\N言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.05,0:30:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be late for school.\N我上學快遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.74,0:30:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Michael? Is he okay?\N麥克怎麼樣  他還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.08,0:30:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've spoken to him.\N我跟他談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.83,0:30:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He understands.\N他知道輕重
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.37,0:30:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's tough...\N第一次看到這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...seeing that for the first time. Well, you turned out.\N他一定相當震驚  不過  你已經熬過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.30,0:30:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't protect them forever.\N你不可能永遠保護他們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.14,0:30:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't this, it'd be something else.\N他遲早會經歷這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.31,0:30:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natural law.\N自然法則
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.15,0:31:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sons are put on this earth to trouble their fathers.\N兒子生來就是替老子找麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.29,0:31:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John's also made it clear that Finn McGovern's operation...\N約翰交代得很清楚  芬恩·麥高文的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.21,0:31:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be divided up locally...\N將打散
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.33,0:31:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...among two territories that John will select personally.\N併入兩個約翰親自挑選的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.51,0:31:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take this moment to thank Mr. Rance for...\N在此特別感謝藍斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...interrupting a busy travel schedule to pay us a visit.\N百忙之中抽空前來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.35,0:31:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Jack.\N謝謝  傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.10,0:31:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rance met with John and me earlier to make another bid...\N藍斯先生跟約翰和我談過
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.14,0:31:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for our involvement in the unions.\N他再次邀請我們加入工會
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.48,0:31:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I told Mr. Rance what I told him before:\N我跟藍斯先生重申我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.65,0:31:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What men do after work is what made us rich.\N男人們下班後的活動讓我們賺飽了荷包
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.57,0:31:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to screw them at work as well.\N沒必要再去剝削他們的勞力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.57,0:31:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is there any other business? - Yes.\N- 還有其他事情嗎  - 有
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.95,0:32:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connor, is there something you would like to say about last night?\N康諾  昨晚的事報告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.84,0:32:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to apologize for what happened.\N昨天的事  我想先道個歉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.89,0:32:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially to you, Pa.\N特別是對你  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.51,0:32:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two wakes in a month... What can I say?\N一個月辦兩次喪事  我能說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.60,0:32:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost a good man last night.\N我們損失了一位好弟兄
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.81,0:32:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's funny?\N你覺得好笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.69,0:32:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try again.\N重說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.45,0:32:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to apologize--\N我想表達歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.66,0:32:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would like to apologize? Try again.\N你想表達歉意  重說
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.68,0:33:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen...\N在座的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.73,0:33:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my apologies.\N謹致深深的歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.78,0:33:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone clear about bit borrowers?\N各位清楚我們對小額貸款的立場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.74,0:33:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been far too many debts outstanding.\N欠債不還的人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.87,0:33:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mike... - Just give me their names.\N- 麥克  - 名單給我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.87,0:33:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me who to visit.\N跟我說該找誰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.12,0:33:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, gentlemen.\N謝謝各位出席
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.29,0:33:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on upstairs.\N上樓來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.50,0:34:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不跟別人打架
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.18,0:34:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike.\N麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.14,0:34:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad forgot to give you this.\N爸忘了把這交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.90,0:34:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a reminder for Tony Calvino. He's light again.\N給湯尼·卡維諾的信函  他又拖欠債款了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.74,0:34:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming?\N你來不來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.53,0:34:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm under house arrest for a while.\N不  我暫時被禁足了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.53,0:34:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm sorry about last night. I am.\N昨晚的事我很抱歉  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.33,0:34:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was... Yeah.\N我本來  你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.50,0:34:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\N沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.81,0:35:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Help you, sir? Or just looking? - Here to see Tony Calvino.\N- 有什麼事嗎  先生  - 我來找湯尼·卡維諾
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.57,0:35:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and who are you?\N是嗎  你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.03,0:35:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike Sullivan.\N麥克·蘇利文
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.45,0:35:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.\N沒問題  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.95,0:35:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna frisk me?\N要搜身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.75,0:35:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Should I? - It's a good idea.\N-應該搜嗎  - 應該
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.55,0:35:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only one.\N我只帶一把槍
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.56,0:35:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm a grown man and this place is getting to me.\N我不是小孩  這地方煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.27,0:35:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every night there's trouble.\N每天晚上都有麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.82,0:36:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's got no dough, but all the world's here wasting it.\N全國人民都在遭罪  這裡的人卻揮霍無度
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.57,0:36:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always money for frills and twists, and never money for food.\N有的人富得流油  穿華服  玩美女  有的人則窮得沒飯吃
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.20,0:36:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I despair the species, you know?\N有時我真為人類感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.08,0:36:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 12 in the beauty parlor. Who's the lucky face?\N12號  幸運兒是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.04,0:36:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not from here originally, but jobs ain't hanging off trees, you know.\N我不是本地人  但景氣這麼差  工作不會從天上掉下來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.18,0:36:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a boxer by trade. Nine consecutive titles.\N我是拳擊手  連獲九次冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.68,0:36:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a record in South Orange.\N破了南橘市的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.10,0:36:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd make a pretty good bodyguard, I think.\N當保鏢我想不成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.81,0:36:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is, is Mr. Rooney looking for anyone?\N我是說  隆尼先生缺人手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.57,0:36:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, anyone like me, for example? Is there any chance you might ask him?\N比方說  我這種人  有機會問問他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.11,0:36:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sure. - Thank you, Mr. Sullivan.\N- 當然  - 謝謝  蘇利文先生
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.24,0:36:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much. I appreciate it.\N真是太感謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.00,0:36:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Calvino? Mr. Calvino, Mike Sullivan's here.\N卡維諾先生  卡維諾先生  麥克·蘇利文來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.50,0:37:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shit. - He wants to see you.\N- 糟了  - 他想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.63,0:37:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shit. Is he packing? - Not anymore.\N- 完了  他帶著槍嗎  - 被我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.80,0:37:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\N好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.14,0:37:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him in.\N帶他進來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.81,0:37:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey. You stick around, okay?\N你留在我身邊  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.99,0:37:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\N喂
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.49,0:37:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell are you? Things good with the old man?\N什麼風把你吹來了  老先生還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.78,0:37:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.20,0:37:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here? Don't imagine it's the pussy.\N什麼事竟麻煩你親自上門  該不是來找樂子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.63,0:37:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I have a letter for you from Mr. Rooney. - Am I behind again?\N- 隆尼先生有封信要給你  - 我付款又晚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.76,0:37:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Am I in trouble? - I don't know.\N- 我惹上麻煩了嗎  - 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.00,0:38:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了蘇利文  舊帳一筆勾消
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.16,0:38:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael.\N麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.68,0:39:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!\N不
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.54,0:41:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My God!\N不  老天
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.92,0:42:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pa, I'm sorry. - Stupid!\N- 爸  對不起  - 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.79,0:42:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kid would've talked. I'm sorry.\N那小鬼一定會說出去  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.67,0:42:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn you. Goddamn you!\N上帝詛咒你  上帝詛咒你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.14,0:42:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I curse the fucking day you were born!\N我詛咒你出生的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.98,0:42:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I curse it!\N我詛咒它
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.15,0:42:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!\N你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.16,0:43:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lord.\N噢  主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.70,0:43:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lord. God help us.\N噢  主啊  上帝保佑我們
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.75,0:43:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God help us.\N上帝保佑我們
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.60,0:43:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This house is not our home anymore.\N這房子不再是我們的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.73,0:43:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just an empty building.\N它只是空蕩蕩的屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.17,0:44:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you stay here. You stay out of sight.\N你留在這兒  不要讓人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.34,0:44:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't go, Pa. Don't go. - Michael...\N- 不要走  爸  別走  - 麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.89,0:44:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when they find out we're gone, they're gonna come after us.\N他們發現我們走了一定會追來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.43,0:44:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect you now.\N現在起  我必須保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.48,0:44:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Pa.\N我求你  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.57,0:44:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here, take this.\N好吧  這個拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.03,0:44:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No. I don't want it. - Take it.\N- 我不要  - 拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.65,0:44:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't want it. - Boy, take it! You got six shots.\N- 我不要啊  - 拿著  你有六發子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.12,0:44:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not back in half an hour, go tell Reverend Lynch what's happened.\N我如果半個小時沒回來  去找林奇牧師說出實情
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.83,0:44:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not go to Father Callaway.\N不要找卡拉威神父
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.28,0:45:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any business with you, Mr. Kelly.\N此事跟你無關  凱利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.78,0:45:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have business with you, Mike.\N但我有事找你  麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.62,0:45:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.\N請說
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.29,0:45:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?\N那是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.29,0:45:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25,000 dollars. Mr. Rooney wants you to know there's more if you need it.\N二萬五千美元  隆尼先生說  需要的話還有
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.42,0:45:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have friends in lreland, Mike. Why don't you take Peter and leave?\N你在愛爾蘭有朋友  帶著彼得遠走高飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.76,0:45:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take Peter.\N我沒辦法帶彼得去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.68,0:45:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.\N他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.31,0:45:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So where's Connor? - He's in hiding.\N- 康諾在哪裡  - 躲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.07,0:45:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where? - You know I can't tell you that.\N- 躲在哪裡  - 你知道我不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.57,0:45:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think sticking a gun to my head is gonna make any difference to me?\N你以為拿槍對著我有用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.83,0:45:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell you, I'm a dead man anyway. We both are.\N說出來  我還不是死路一條  我們兩個都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.83,0:46:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think, Mike. Don't be stupid. I'm just the messenger.\N想清楚  麥克  別做傻事  我只是負責傳話
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.18,0:46:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then give Mr. Rooney a message for me.\N那麼幫我帶句話給隆尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.02,0:46:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\N什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.87,0:46:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the gun.\N槍給我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.30,0:46:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?\N我們要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.89,0:46:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Chicago.\N芝加哥
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.18,0:46:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a man there who runs things.\N我認識那裡的一位元大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.64,0:46:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done some work for him.\N以前幫他辦過幾次事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.64,0:47:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find out where he stands.\N我們得請教他的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.19,0:47:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to get some sleep.\N你先睡一會
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.71,0:48:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to wait for me here.\N你在這裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.09,0:48:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sure. - I won't be long. You'll be all right?\N- 當然  - 我很快回來  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.38,0:48:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah, I'll be all right. - That's a good boy.\N- 沒問題  - 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.35,0:49:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello, Mike. - Hello, fellas.\N- 哈囉  麥克  - 哈囉  兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.65,0:49:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to see you. We heard what happened. How you holding up?\N又見面了,我們聽說了,你還撐得住吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.98,0:49:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to Mr. Nitti.\N我想跟尼提先生談談
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.24,0:49:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's awful busy. - I can wait.\N- 他非常忙  - 我可以等
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.99,0:50:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Take the man to the top.\N好  帶這位先生去頂樓
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.39,0:51:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, sir.\N當然  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.65,0:51:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait so long, Mike. Come on in.\N抱歉讓你久等  麥克  請進
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.40,0:51:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all just heard what happened.\N我們剛聽說了你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.03,0:51:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus, I'm sorry, Mike.\N天啊  真遺憾  麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.20,0:51:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you for seeing me, Mr. Nitti.\N謝謝你肯見我  尼提先生
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.83,0:51:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, sit down.\N請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.79,0:51:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Like some coffee or...? - No.\N- 來杯咖啡還是  - 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.33,0:51:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You sure? - Yes, thank you.\N- 你確定嗎  - 是的 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.59,0:51:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what can I do for you, Mike?\N我能怎麼幫你  麥克
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.26,0:51:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to work for you.\N我想為你工作
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.06,0:51:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's very interesting.\N這倒有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.14,0:51:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in return, I'd like you to turn a blind eye to what I have to do.\N作為回報  我希望您不要干涉我的私事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.19,0:51:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is that?\N你想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.82,0:52:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill the man who murdered my family.\N宰了殺我妻兒的兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.20,0:52:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is one more body gonna make a difference?\N多死一個人有什麼不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.00,0:52:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good proposal, Mr. Nitti.\N這份提議對你很有利  尼提先生
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.92,0:52:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will work only for you, and you know I can do a good job.\N我只為你工作  我是個中高手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.92,0:52:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I respect you, Mike. I do.\N我尊敬你  麥克  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.72,0:52:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would like nothing more than to have you come work for us. But not like this.\N我巴不得你為我效命  但不是在這種情況之下
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.05,0:52:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're asking me is impossible.\N你的要求根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.35,0:52:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?\N是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.10,0:52:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain something to you that maybe you haven't realized.\N讓我為你解釋清楚  或許有些事情你不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.57,0:52:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these years, you've been living under the protection...\N多年來  許多關心你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.49,0:52:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of people who care about you.\N一直在保護著你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.91,0:52:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those same people are protecting you now, including me.\N同一批人現在還在保護你  包括我
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.54,0:52:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you go ahead with this, if you open that door...\N如果你一意孤行  打開那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.67,0:52:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're walking through it alone.\N你得孤獨地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.59,0:53:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all that loyalty, all that trust, will no longer exist for you.\N所謂的忠誠  信任  對你來說不再存在
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.26,0:53:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mike, you won't make it. Not on your own.\N而且  麥克  你不可能成功  單槍匹馬不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.60,0:53:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And not with a little boy.\N帶著小孩更不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.61,0:53:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're protecting him already?\N你已經開始保護他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.74,0:53:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're protecting our interests, Mike.\N我們是在保護我們的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.50,0:53:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drove all through the night to see you.\N我連夜驅車前來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.96,0:53:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that. Now I suggest you drive yourself back.\N謝謝  我建議你再趕回去
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.76,0:53:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, Mike. Go home and bury your wife and child.\N回家吧  麥克  好好安葬妻小
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.52,0:53:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our blessing.\N我們祝福你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.85,0:53:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be that simple.\N事情沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.77,0:54:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard?\N你們聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.77,0:54:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, listen to me. He's in the building.\N爸爸  聽我說  趁他在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.03,0:54:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You can end this now. Take him now. - Connor, get upstairs.\N- 你可以做個了結  殺了他  - 康諾  上樓去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.92,0:55:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God help me.\N上帝幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.21,0:55:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God help me. What do I do?\N上帝幫幫我  我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.38,0:55:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think objectively.\N客觀地想清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.35,0:55:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you make your choice.\N然後做出抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.10,0:55:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if Sullivan were just some guy?\N如果蘇利文是個陌生人  你會怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.98,0:55:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God help me.\N上帝幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.03,0:55:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Make it quick. - And the kid?\N- 一定要乾淨俐落  - 那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.78,0:55:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Christ. No, no.\N噢  老天  不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.62,0:55:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day the kid becomes a man... Think he won't remember?\N你以為他長大後會忘記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.92,0:55:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said not the kid.\N我說了  不能殺那小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.59,0:55:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.21,0:55:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who to call.\N我知道該找誰
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.47,0:55:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a guy who's done some work for us in the past.\N一個過去幫過我們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.85,0:55:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gifted.\N他極具天賦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.28,0:56:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, ma'am. Press. Press.\N抱歉  女士  我是媒體記者  媒體記者
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.45,0:56:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was raping my wife. He raped my wife.\N他強暴我太太
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.12,0:56:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, you're treading on the evidence here.\N跟我來  你踩到證物了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.13,0:56:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two minutes.\N只要兩分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.67,0:56:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Mr. Maguire.\N沒問題  馬蓋爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.97,0:58:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harlen Maguire. Good evening, Mr. Nitti.\N哈倫·馬蓋爾  晚安  尼提先生
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.43,0:58:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen hundred.\N一千六百美元
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.60,0:58:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen hundred dollars is my rate, Mr. Nitti.\N我的價碼是一千六  尼提先生
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.40,0:58:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what I make on the photographs is mine.\N照片是我自己賺的外快
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.49,0:58:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never met him.\N沒見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.24,0:58:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know his work.\N但聽說過他的傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.25,0:58:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He traveling alone?\N他獨來獨往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.00,0:58:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old?\N多大年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.39,0:58:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do with the kid?\N小孩怎麼處理
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.90,0:58:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will do.\N就照你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.86,0:58:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.07,0:59:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember your aunt Sarah? Your mom's sister?\N你記得莎拉姨媽嗎  你母親的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.87,0:59:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lives in Perdition. She'll take you in.\N住在派迪遜  她肯讓你跟她住
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.92,0:59:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?\N她家在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.05,0:59:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right by the lake.\N湖邊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.76,0:59:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went there once, all of us, when you were 4, maybe 5.\N我們全家去過一次  你四五歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.60,0:59:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.\N風景很美
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.85,0:59:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember?\N記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.40,0:59:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place with the dog.\N她家有狗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.11,1:01:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello? - Sarah.\N- 哈囉  - 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.73,1:01:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike. Oh, thank God.\N麥克  噢  感謝上帝
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.69,1:01:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know we're okay.\N只是跟你報個平安
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.07,1:01:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?\N你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.82,1:01:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way to your place, if that's all right.\N正在去你家的路上  如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.03,1:01:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I'll be back there in two days.\N當然  我兩天后回去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.45,1:01:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Michael?\N麥克還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.87,1:01:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's all right.\N他還好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.88,1:02:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?\N喪事辦得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.55,1:02:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mike...\N噢  麥克
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.76,1:02:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?\N哈囉
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.06,1:02:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see you soon.\N見面再談
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.25,1:02:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello, operator? - Yes, sir.\N- 哈囉  接線生  - 是的  先生
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.21,1:02:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just cut off, could you reconnect me?\N剛斷線了  麻煩幫我重接
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.20,1:03:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hungry?\N肚子餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.78,1:03:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不餓
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.66,1:04:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might not be another diner for a while, so you should eat.\N前面可能很遠都不會再有餐館
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.29,1:04:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hungry.\N我不餓
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.08,1:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanna read.\N我只想看書
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.86,1:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Slow night, huh? - You kidding? This is busy.\N- 生意挺清淡的嘛  - 開玩笑  算忙了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.49,1:05:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What can I get you? - You got a special?\N- 要點什麼  - 有特餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.78,1:05:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's special.\N每樣東西都很特別
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.33,1:06:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is that so? - Everything except the food.\N- 是嗎  - 除了食物以外
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.41,1:06:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything except the food?\N除了食物以外都很特別
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.92,1:06:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You ought to be on the stage. - Don't I know it.\N- 你應該從事演藝工作  - 可不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.92,1:06:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some of that honey-dipped fried chicken and a black coffee.\N我要蜜汁炸雞和一杯黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.72,1:06:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duck soup.\N馬上來
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.77,1:06:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me, sir.\N不用理我  先生
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.81,1:06:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a free country. Used to be, anyhow.\N這是自由國度  曾經是啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.53,1:06:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you, sir.\N不  謝謝你  先生
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.83,1:06:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your profession or your pleasure?\N那是你的職業還是消遣
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.76,1:06:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both, I guess.\N應該說兩者皆是
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.18,1:07:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be paid to do what you love.... Ain't that the dream?\N既喜愛又有錢賺  豈不完美
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.98,1:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.\N說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.69,1:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yourself?\N你呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.19,1:07:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a salesman. Machine parts.\N銷售員  機械零件
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.53,1:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machine parts.\N機械零件
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.66,1:07:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's wonderful. - I assure you, it is not.\N- 好工作  - 跟你說  一點都不好
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.70,1:07:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So who do you work for? - Can you keep a secret?\N- 你在什麼公司上班  - 可以幫我保守秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.42,1:07:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm press.\N我是媒體記者
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.75,1:07:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which paper?\N哪家報社
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.88,1:07:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All over. I'm something of a rarity.\N很多家  我從事的是罕見的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.09,1:07:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?\N怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.72,1:07:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shoot the dead.\N我幫死人照相
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.60,1:07:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead bodies, that is. I don't kill them.\N屍體啦  人不是我殺的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.19,1:07:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should hope not.\N我想應該不是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.82,1:08:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always fascinated me, the look of them, you know?\N死人的樣子令我很著迷  有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.24,1:08:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You ever seen one? - Yeah.\N- 你見過死人嗎  - 見過
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.96,1:08:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for you.\N我為你感到難過
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.25,1:08:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible thing.\N恐怖的經驗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.88,1:08:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sure makes you feel alive, don't it?\N但讓你感覺活著真好  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.64,1:08:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drink to that.\N值得為此幹一杯
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.14,1:08:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff makes you sweat, huh?\N它令你直冒汗呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.44,1:08:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, piss too.\N對  是啊  而且利尿
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.90,1:08:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, ma'am, can you help me out here?\N對不起  小姐  洗手間在哪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.44,1:08:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just through here.\N從這裡走過去
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.90,1:08:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\N喂
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.78,1:08:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, there.\N小心
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.88,1:09:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thanks, Ruby. - Good night.\N- 謝謝你  露比  - 晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.20,1:09:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot to leave a tip.\N忘了放小費了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.80,1:09:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get down. - Why? What's going on?\N- 趴下  - 為什麼  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.34,1:09:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!\N趴下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.09,1:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think you're--?\N嘿  你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.45,1:10:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the car.\N下車
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.95,1:10:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the car! When I say get down, you get down.\N出來  我說趴下就趴下
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.58,1:10:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask questions. When I say we're stopping to eat, you stay with me.\N沒有為什麼  吃東西時  一定得跟在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.84,1:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listen to me from now on, or you start taking care of yourself.\N聽話  不然你得自己照顧自己
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.30,1:10:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can take care of myself fine! You never wanted me along anyway.\N我可以照顧自己  反正你根本不想帶著我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.30,1:10:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You think it's my fault this happened. - Stop it.\N- 你認為這全是我的錯  - 住口
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.35,1:10:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was not your fault!\N那不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.39,1:10:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of this is your fault.\N所有事情都不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.56,1:10:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Just take me to Aunt Sarah's. - I can't take you there.\N- 帶我去莎拉阿姨家就對了  - 我不能帶你去那兒
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.23,1:10:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now.\N現在不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.90,1:10:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why? - He knows that's where we're going.\N- 為什麼  - 他知道我們要去那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.24,1:10:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you gonna do?\N那你想怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.46,1:10:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I can't do alone.\N接下來的事我一個人辦不成
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.71,1:11:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to listen to me now, okay?\N你一定要好好聽我的話  知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.55,1:11:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else both of us are dead.\N不然我們兩個都活不了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.51,1:11:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make Capone give up Connor.\N我得逼卡彭放棄康諾
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.43,1:11:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing Chicago loves more than anything...\N現在芝加哥幫派份子只關心一樣東西
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.98,1:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's their money.\N錢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.77,1:11:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got it in banks all over the state. We have to find it and take it.\N他們將錢存在州內各銀行  我們把它找出來  拿走
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.98,1:11:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you gonna help me? - Yes.\N- 你要幫我嗎  - 好
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.91,1:11:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have to teach you something.\N那麼我就要教你幾樣功夫
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.62,1:11:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You know what the clutch is? - Sure I know what the clutch is.\N- 知不知道什麼是離合器  - 當然知道
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.46,1:11:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is the clutch? - The clutch, it... It clutches.\N- 離合器是什麼  - 就離合器嘛  幫助離合
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.63,1:11:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, it clutches. Which of those pedals is the clutch?\N對  幫助離合  哪一個踏板是離合器
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.80,1:11:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the gas.\N那是油門
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.80,1:11:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gas. I'll show you.\N加速的油門
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.59,1:11:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There. Right there, see?\N我來教你  看到沒
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.30,1:11:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the clutch, and it does the clutching.\N離合器幫助你進檔  退檔
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.65,1:12:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go again.\N再來一次
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.74,1:12:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release gas, clutch, shift gear, hit gas...\N松油門  踩離合器  換檔  踩油門
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.16,1:12:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shift.\N換檔
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.22,1:12:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Can I make one suggestion? - No.\N- 我可以給你個建議嗎  - 不用
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.93,1:12:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this.\N我要自己做
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.23,1:12:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, 45 miles an hour, that's a little fast.\N時速45英里  太快了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.74,1:12:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out for the tractor, Mike.\N小心那輛牽引機  麥克
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.20,1:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael, look out for the tractor.\N麥克  小心那輛牽引機
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.24,1:12:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for the tractor. Watch out for the tractor!\N小心那輛牽引機  小心那輛牽引機
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.54,1:13:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We made it. - Oh, yeah, yeah, we made it.\N- 我們成功了  - 對  對  成功了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.68,1:13:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more excuses. I've told you once, now I'm telling you again--\N沒有理由  我不再說了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.81,1:13:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm looking for a Mr. McDougal. -Just one moment.\N- 我找麥道格先生  - 請稍等
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.15,1:13:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a pleasant surprise.\N真是意外的驚喜
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.90,1:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting another deposit until the end of the month.\N我以為這個月不會有存款了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.20,1:13:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm making a withdrawal. I want dirty money only.\N事實上  我是來取款的  我只拿髒錢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.20,1:13:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you're holding for Capone that's off the books. Open the safe.\N卡彭的每一分錢都不能少  保險櫃打開
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.75,1:13:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're insane. You know they'll find out who you are.\N你瘋了  他們一定知道你是誰
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.42,1:13:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Sullivan. You want me to spell it?\N大名蘇利文  要我寫下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.26,1:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the box.\N箱子打開
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.93,1:13:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll kill you. They're animals.\N他們會殺了你  他們是野獸
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.59,1:14:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say. Put it in.\N是嗎  放進去
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.06,1:14:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for you.\N這疊是給你的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.48,1:14:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call it a handling charge. Tell Chicago I took it.\N算手續費  跟芝加哥說我拿的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.11,1:14:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I read about this in the papers, if I read about the savings of farmers...\N但如果我在報上看到無辜農夫的血汗錢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.40,1:14:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being wiped out by a heartless bank robber, I won't be happy.\N被搶匪搶走  我會不高興
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.37,1:14:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.\N午安
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.79,1:14:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really trust me not to say anything?\N相信我不會供出你嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.29,1:14:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always trust a bank manager.\N銀行經理最值得信賴
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.18,1:14:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no rush.\N你還真慢條斯理
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.18,1:16:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Coffee? - Thank you.\N- 咖啡  - 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.48,1:16:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what brings you guys to the middle of nowhere?\N怎麼會來這鳥不生蛋的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.27,1:16:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're bank robbers.\N我們是銀行搶匪
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.57,1:16:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just passing through.\N只是路過
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.16,1:16:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when do I get my share of the money?\N我的那份什麼時候給我
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.25,1:16:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how much do you want?\N你要多少
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.59,1:16:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two hundred dollars.\N兩百美元
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.01,1:16:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Deal.\N沒問題  說定了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.52,1:16:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Could I have had more? - You'll never know.\N- 我如果多要  你會給我嗎  - 天機不可洩漏
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.41,1:17:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on.\N快接啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.68,1:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much did they take?\N他們拿走了多少
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.14,1:17:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much?\N多少
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.77,1:17:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, answer me this: What are we paying you for?\N回答我  我們付錢給你幹嘛的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.57,1:17:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where's my father? - What's this?\N- 我父親呢  - 搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.61,1:17:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is no one talking to me? I feel like a fucking prisoner.\N沒人願意跟我說話嗎  好像我是個犯人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.24,1:17:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. You are not a prisoner. You are being protected.\N你不是犯人  你在戒護中
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.16,1:17:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This is what your father wants. - I can look after myself.\N- 令尊交代的  - 我會照顧自己
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.58,1:17:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't. This is the point.\N不  你不會  這就是重點
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.21,1:17:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a big baby who doesn't know his thumb from his dick.\N你連拇指跟老二都分不清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.13,1:18:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you.\N去你的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.59,1:18:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason you're still alive is because you're John Rooney's son.\N聽清楚  小子  要不是你爹  你能活到現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.51,1:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being a little shortsighted here, Frank.\N別太短視近利  法蘭克
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.01,1:18:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is an old man.\N我爸是個老頭
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.31,1:18:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the future.\N而我是未來
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.52,1:18:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't you ever talk to me that way again.\N不要用那種態度跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.54,1:18:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maguire, do what you have to. Find them.\N馬蓋爾  想辦法把他們找出來
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.71,1:18:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mr. Sullivan, there is no money.\N對不起  蘇利文先生  沒有錢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.96,1:18:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No-- I can get you money, I just--\N我是說  我可以幫你弄錢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.97,1:18:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be Chicago's.\N但  不是芝加哥的錢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.55,1:18:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took it all out two days ago.\N他們兩天前提光了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.18,1:18:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who authorized it? - The accountant.\N- 誰授權的  - 會計師
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.73,1:18:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his name?\N叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.77,1:19:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mr. Rance in the bridal suite.\N我是蜜月套房的藍斯先生
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.32,1:19:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you proffer your congratulations, there's no Mrs. Rance with me...\N不用虛情假意的道賀  這裡沒有藍斯太太
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.90,1:19:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'm all the better for it. Listen carefully...\N我很慶倖  你仔細聽好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.45,1:19:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I am in no mood.\N我心情不好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.20,1:19:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to say this only once.\N我只說一次
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.50,1:19:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like a boiled egg, and I want it runny.\N我要水煮蛋  蛋黃半熟
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.75,1:19:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa, can we sleep in a motel room tonight instead of the car?\N爸  我們可以睡汽車旅館  而不是睡車上嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.67,1:19:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that would be nice.\N好啊  這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.68,1:19:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many more days you gonna want me, mister?\N你還要我陪你幾天  先生
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.06,1:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we close the curtains, even for a little while?\N窗簾可以拉上嗎  就一會兒
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.07,1:19:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get no sleep with all that light.\N這麼亮我睡不著
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.82,1:19:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see anything, you hit that horn twice.\N發現任何異狀  按兩次喇叭
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.70,1:19:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get out of the car, no matter what.\N絕對不要下車
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.34,1:20:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.\N再見
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.34,1:20:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ready? - I'm ready.\N- 準備好了嗎  - 好了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.11,1:20:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Right away, sir.\N是的  先生  馬上
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.74,1:20:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Runny.\N半熟
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.18,1:20:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open.\N門沒鎖
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.59,1:20:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Top marks for speed, no marks for cookery.\N速度一流  品質不入流
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.72,1:21:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, may I ask, do you call this?\N請問這叫做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.60,1:21:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it down.\N放下
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.02,1:21:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Sullivan. - Mr. Rance.\N- 蘇利文先生  - 藍斯先生
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.53,1:21:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find me?\N你怎麼找到我的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.36,1:21:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best hotel in the area. And you are so very...particular.\N這是本區最高級的飯店  而你總是那麼特別
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.62,1:21:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed, Mr. Sullivan.\N說得沒錯  蘇利文先生
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.95,1:21:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you to lower your weapon.\N可以放下武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.54,1:21:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Now, what do you want?\N謝謝  有何貴幹
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.96,1:21:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information.\N情報
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.01,1:21:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give you the files.\N資料不能給你
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.26,1:21:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right.\N好  好
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.18,1:21:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the next room.\N東西在隔壁房間
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.73,1:21:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- In here. - Bring it in.\N- 在這裡  - 拿過來
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.91,1:21:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see.\N我看不見
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.54,1:22:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you accomplish by interfering with our business?\N你干涉我們的買賣有何意義
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.75,1:22:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This has nothing to do with business. - It's all business. You fail to grasp that.\N- 此事跟買賣無關  - 怎麼會無關  只是你不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.26,1:22:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in business, you must have something to trade.\N所謂買賣  一定得有東西交換
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.17,1:22:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Mr. Sullivan, have nothing to trade.\N你  蘇利文先生  沒東西交換
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.76,1:22:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially not for anyone as valuable as Connor Rooney.\N尤其是交換昂貴的康諾·隆尼
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.76,1:22:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.\N我不懂
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.23,1:22:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening bell on Wall Street.\N華爾街開盤了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.86,1:22:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, open it.\N打開
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.69,1:22:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is it?\N哪把鑰匙來著
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.46,1:22:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, not it.\N不對  不對  不是這把
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.51,1:23:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tried that one already.\N這把試過了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.31,1:23:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better start over.\N最好重試一次
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.60,1:23:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got one more try.\N你只剩一次機會
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.48,1:23:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.\N噢  找到了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.10,1:24:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. Watch the road!\N我還好  專心看路
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.58,1:24:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa! Pa, are you okay?\N爸  爸  你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.46,1:24:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa!\N爸
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.90,1:24:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa!\N爸
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.60,1:25:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!\N救命
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.10,1:25:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us!\N救救我們
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.06,1:25:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!\N救命
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.08,1:25:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!\N救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.74,1:25:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us!\N救救我們
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.08,1:26:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you two heading out?\N你們兩個什麼時候離開
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.88,1:26:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've stayed long enough.\N我知道打擾你們很久了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.96,1:26:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna cause you any trouble.\N我不想為您惹來麻煩
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.72,1:26:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No trouble so far.\N目前還沒有麻煩
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.89,1:26:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good worker.\N他是個好幫手
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.40,1:26:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have any kids?\N你有孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.23,1:26:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.36,1:26:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We met too late.\N我們相識得太晚
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.07,1:26:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He dotes on you.\N他非常愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.70,1:26:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't see it.\N你沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.61,1:27:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.\N哈囉
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.91,1:27:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bad dream.\N我作了一個惡夢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.08,1:27:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna talk about it?\N想說給我聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.54,1:27:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come on in. Take a seat...\N進來吧  坐下聊聊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.54,1:27:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you want.\N如果你想的話
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.77,1:27:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Math, huh?\N你在算數學嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.10,1:27:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N對
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.06,1:28:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always hated it.\N我最討厭數學
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.11,1:28:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.\N我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.28,1:28:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you like?\N那你喜歡什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.45,1:28:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\N什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.24,1:28:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What subjects do you like--? Did you like...in school?\N你在學校的時候  喜歡什麼科目
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.79,1:28:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bible history, maybe.\N聖經歷史  可能吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.80,1:28:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\N為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.01,1:28:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the stories.\N我喜歡那些故事
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.47,1:28:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter was good at math.\N彼得數學很厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.77,1:28:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he?\N是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.15,1:28:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you like Peter more than me?\N你是不是更喜歡彼得  而不是我
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.53,1:28:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不會啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.50,1:29:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Michael.\N不會啦  麥克
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.79,1:29:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved you both the same.\N你們兩個我都愛
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.01,1:29:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were...\N但是  你
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.93,1:29:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were different with me.\N對我不一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.72,1:29:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I?\N是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.86,1:29:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.53,1:29:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was because Peter was just such a sweet boy, you know?\N可能因為彼得比較可愛
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.87,1:29:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you...\N而你
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.04,1:29:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were more like me.\N你比較像我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.63,1:29:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't want you to be.\N而我並不希望你像我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.14,1:30:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to be...different.\N我不是有意  偏心
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.40,1:30:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.95,1:30:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Pa.\N晚安  爸
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.91,1:30:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.\N晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.43,1:31:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芬恩·麥高文之帳戶
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.28,1:31:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康諾·隆尼之存款收據
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.65,1:31:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael, wake up. Get your things.\N麥克  醒醒  收拾行李
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.82,1:31:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving.\N我們要走了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.41,1:31:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We left you something.\N我們留了點東西給你們
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.02,1:32:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, John.\N你好  約翰
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.57,1:33:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a smart man, Michael.\N你真不簡單  麥克
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.87,1:33:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna talk.\N我想跟你談談
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.71,1:33:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?\N在這兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.46,1:33:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Downstairs.\N樓下
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.99,1:33:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd see you again.\N沒想到還會再見面
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.12,1:33:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read this.\N拿去看看
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.00,1:33:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connor's been stealing from you for years.\N康諾偷你的錢好幾年了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.63,1:34:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He keeps accounts open under the names of dead men. Men like the McGoverns.\N他用死人的名義開通了帳戶  比如說麥高文家人
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.80,1:34:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stood there and helped him kill Finn to line his own pockets.\N我幫他殺了芬恩  沒想到卻是在幫他賺黑心錢
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.64,1:34:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was working for you, but I wasn't.\N我以為我替你工作  其實不然
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.60,1:34:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd give up my son?\N你以為我會放棄我兒子嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.73,1:34:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was betraying you.\N他背叛了你
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.27,1:34:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.\N我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.65,1:34:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, listen to me.\N聽我說
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.94,1:34:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to avoid more bloodshed. You wouldn't accept that...\N我曾嘗試避免流血  可你不接受
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.11,1:34:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I did what was necessary. But I've always loved you like a son.\N那我只能下狠手  但我一直把你當兒子看
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.49,1:34:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'm telling you, leave before it's too late.\N現在我警告你  趁來得及  快走
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.50,1:34:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think.\N想一想
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.58,1:34:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're protecting him now, but when you're gone, they won't need him.\N他們目前保護他  但當你走後  他們就不再需要他了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.21,1:34:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This ends with Connor dead regardless. - That may be...\N- 康諾橫豎是死路一條  - 很可能如此
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.09,1:34:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you are asking me...\N但你是要求我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.18,1:34:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to give you the key to his room so you can walk in...\N把他的房間鑰匙給你
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.85,1:34:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...put a gun to his head and pull the trigger. I can't do that.\N讓你用槍射穿他腦袋  我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.52,1:35:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He murdered Annie and Peter. - There are only murderers in this room.\N- 他謀殺了安妮和彼得  - 這裡哪一個不是殺人兇手
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.44,1:35:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael, open your eyes.\N麥克  張開眼睛看清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.53,1:35:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the life we chose, the life we lead.\N我們選擇了這種生活  就得過這種生活
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.20,1:35:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is only one guarantee: None of us will see heaven.\N只有一項保證  我們誰都上不了天堂
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.87,1:35:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael could.\N麥克可以
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.25,1:35:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do everything that you can to see that that happens.\N那麼  你就盡你所能確定你能達成心願
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.55,1:35:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave. I'm begging you.\N走吧  我求你
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.93,1:35:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only way.\N這是唯一的路
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.93,1:35:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I go?\N如果我真的走呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.85,1:35:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...\N那麼
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.98,1:35:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will mourn...\N我將哀悼
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.90,1:35:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the son I lost.\N我的喪子之痛
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.63,1:36:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?\N你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.30,1:36:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one last thing, and then it's done.\N再做一件事就全部了結了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.97,1:36:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to bed, Michael.\N回去睡覺
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.04,1:37:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給麥克
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.76,1:40:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it's you.\N我很慶倖是你
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.71,1:41:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.\N我瞭解
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.55,1:41:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Al wants your assurance that after that, it's over.\N但艾爾希望你保證這件事之後  一了百了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.80,1:41:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lexington Hotel, room 1432.\N萊辛頓飯店  1432房
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.65,1:45:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the house?\N就是那棟房子嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.40,1:45:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.\N沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.86,1:45:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew there was a dog.\N我就知道有一隻狗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.82,1:46:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah? It's me, Mike. We're here.\N莎拉  是我  麥克  我們到了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.17,1:47:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile.\N笑一個
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.62,1:48:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the gun.\N把槍給我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.79,1:48:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael.\N麥克
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.62,1:48:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael...\N麥克
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.71,1:48:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't you do this.\N不要開槍
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.84,1:48:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the gun, Michael.\N把槍給我  麥克
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.55,1:48:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.\N快點
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.76,1:48:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the gun.\N把槍給我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.53,1:49:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do it.\N我下不了手
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.82,1:49:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.\N我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.17,1:49:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pa. - I'm sorry.\N- 爸  - 對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.63,1:49:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.\N對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.68,1:49:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\N對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.39,1:49:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa.\N爸
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.06,1:49:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa!\N爸
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.58,1:49:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa!\N爸
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.54,1:49:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa.\N爸
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.50,1:49:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa! Pa!\N爸  爸
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.17,1:50:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw then that my father's only fear...\N我看見父親唯一的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.68,1:50:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was that his son would follow the same road.\N就是兒子步上他的後塵
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.23,1:50:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was the last time I ever held a gun.\N那是我最後一次拿槍
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.63,1:51:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People always thought I grew up on a farm.\N人們以為我在農場長大
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.39,1:51:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I guess, in a way, I did.\N而我想  從某方面來看  這也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.90,1:51:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I lived a lifetime before that...\N但在那之前的六周逃亡路上
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.86,1:51:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in those six weeks on the road...\N我經歷了我的整個人生
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.86,1:51:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the winter of 1931.\N當時是1931年冬天
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.46,1:52:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When people ask me if Michael Sullivan was a good man...\N當別人問我  麥克·蘇利文是不是個好人
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.13,1:52:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or if there was just no good in him at all...\N或者  他是不是無惡不作
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.38,1:52:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I always give the same answer.\N我的答案永遠一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.43,1:52:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just tell them...\N我只跟他們說
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.27,1:52:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."He was my father."\N他是我父親
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.48,1:52:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謹以本片深沉紀念\N康 拉 德 · L · 赫 爾\N生於1926年  卒於2003年
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.80,1:52:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康拉德·L·赫爾  本片攝影指導  這是他生前最後一部掌鏡電影


